{
  "stem": "17761.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went Motza'ei Shabbat from Bucharest by train to a place called [INAUDIBLE], which is all the Donau, on the Danube, which holds a very wide river.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the night, we were shipped over to the Bulgarian coast in a place called Rusciciuk, R-U-S-C-I-C-I-- Rus-- --C-I-U-K.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I even remember the song that I sang at that passage on the Donau, which is talking about a little ship floating on the-- on the waters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we came at this-- at the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the way, on my shoulder was this little Sefer Torah that I carried with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I carried it back to my city, to my little town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took it when I went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took it with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was my [INAUDIBLE], they said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, we had to walk a long tunnel-- I remember that we were exhausted-- until we finally saw the wagons of the Bulgarian railways.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the middle each wagon, there was bread, and water, and wonderful grapes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I immediately made the comparison between the same wagons many years ago, when we went and we were deported.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these trains brought us to a place called Burgars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a port.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "B-U-R-G-A-R-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there, at the end-- at the eve of Yom Kippur, 1947-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we arrived there day by train around 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And during two or three hours, 2,400 people were squeezed in in a little boat like sardines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had-- everybody had to lie down until everybody's on ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And immediately after this has been done, the ship started to-- to-- to take off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I'll never forget these two-- the majority of these people standing on the deck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There wasn't where to sit or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
